column4: I want to play MIDI files but can't.  First it said "no such device /dev/snd/seq", so I modprobed snd-seq.  Now it says its playing but I don't hear any sound.  I can hear Waveform sounds but not MIDI.  What could the problem be?
WickedPuppy, in KDE, when you press ALT+F2, the "Run Command" box comes up
